Package: imo
Title: Ion Mirror Optimization
Version: 0.1.0.9007
Authors@R: c(
  person("Patrick", "Sturm", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
          email = "sturm@tofwerk.com"),
  person("TOFWERK", role = c("cph", "fnd")))
Description: The R package provides functions to optimize the geometry and 
  voltages of planar or axially symmetric ion mirrors, where the potential can 
  be calculated analytically. Design of expriments (DoE) and response surface 
  methodology (RSM) is used for efficient optimization.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/pasturm/imo
BugReports: https://github.com/pasturm/imo/issues
Imports: rsm, RcppTOML, plotly, gplots, foreach, doParallel, gsl
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
